Class ScriptTargetMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.util.ScriptTargetMapping

  • public class ScriptTargetMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a relation between a file in workspace IFile and a script on remote VM VmResource. A file may participate in several mappings simultaneously.
